  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed part first floor rear extension by reason of its size, scale, width, height and design would result in an incongruous, dominant, disproportionate, bulky and visually intrusive addition that would fail to harmonise with the architectural composition of the original dwelling and would fail to preserve or enhance the character and appearance of the West Drayton Green Conservation Area. Therefore, the proposal would be contrary to Policy BE1 of the Hillingdon Local Plan: Part One - Strategic Policies (November 2012) and Policies DMHB 4, DMHB 11, DMHB 12 and DMHD 1 of the Hillingdon Local Plan: Part Two - Development Management Policies (January 2020)."
